msgid ""
"As a second step, we want to create a directory with each translated file "
"per target language (in this example we are using Spanish/Argentina and "
"Portuguese/Brazil). This can be achieved with the following command:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/manage-translations-sphinx.rst:77
msgid "sphinx-intl update -p _build/gettext -l es_AR -l pt_BR"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../guides/manage-translations-sphinx.rst:78
msgid ""
"This command will create a directory structure similar to the following "
"(with one ``.po`` file per ``.rst`` file in your documentation)::"
